f\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/24.17-19?lang=eng#p18\">Alma 24:18 (17–19)</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"12\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note12a\" data-full-marker=\"12a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128353684\" id=\"note12a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/27.23?lang=eng#p23\">Alma 27:23</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"13\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note13a\" data-full-marker=\"13a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128353686\" id=\"note13a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/affliction?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Affliction</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/tribulation?lang=eng\">Tribulation</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note13b\" data-full-marker=\"13b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128353689\" id=\"note13b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/24.17-19?lang=eng#p18\">Alma 24:18 (17–19)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/56.7?lang=eng#p7\">56:7</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"14\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note14a\" data-full-marker=\"14a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128353691\" id=\"note14a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/num/30.2?lang=eng#p2\">Num. 30:2</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note14b\" data-full-marker=\"14b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128353693\" id=\"note14b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/oath?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Oath</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"16\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note16a\" data-full-m